n to the rite of passage inherent in every pregnancy confirmation.","location":"Waimea","rating":5,"lat":20.020339,"lng":-155.669835,"tier":"free","externalBookingUrl":"","island":"big_island","updatedAt":"2026-04-03T00:36:18.27912+00:00","verified":false},{"id":"50cbc33f-b3c8-43e0-9f48-d8db273d79f0","name":"Seuoka Kelly","image":"https://www.hamakua-health.org/wp-content/uploads/elementor/thumbs/Honokaa-Clinic-pwukaue2aa2smd5k65oywnn6hvd3wphqqoai70b30g.png","type":"practitioner","modality":"Midwife, Psychotherapy, Women's Health","modalities":["Midwife","Psychotherapy","Women's Health"],"sessionType":"in_person","acceptsNewClients":true,"bio":"Hamakua-Kohala Health provides quality healthcare and wellness programs to the North Hawaii Communities. New patients welcome.","location":"Honokaa","rating":5,"lat":20.075967,"lng":-155.470173,"tier":"free","externalBookingUrl":"","island":"big_island","updatedAt":"2026-04-02T09:31:30.328449+00:00","verified":false},{"id":"dda686f3-aa8d-4fa2-a956-b2ffe95cbf9e","name":"Physical Therapy.","businessName":"Pure Fit Physical Therapy and Pelvic Health","image":"https://framerusercontent.com/images/lLsgl4NVWS1UALlBmbjLivUJPPo.png","type":"practitioner","modality":"Physical Therapy, Women's Health","modalities":["Physical Therapy","Women's Health"],"sessionType":"in_person","acceptsNewClients":true,"bio":"Pure Fit physical therpay and pelvic health begins with a simple intention: to help you move with more ease, strength, and trust in your body. Whether youâre healing, rebuilding, or growing, we meet you where you are and guide you forward with care.","location":"Hilo","rating":5,"lat":19.721024,"lng":-155.084329,"tier":"free","externalBookingUrl":"","island":"big_island","updatedAt":"2026-04-02T09:31:30.328449+00:00","verified":false},{"id":"3cbabd6b-02ca-4e9d-8f03-7aaf686929bc","name":"Taylor Hamil","businessName":"Banyan Birth LLC","image":"http://static1.squarespace.com/static/5cba55b3a09a7e30cda8e8be/t/612a8c8da3377b31438ab73